islike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T02:37:24.000Z","msg":"10：33 眾議院選戰，（非正式結果）預期，民主黨暫得69席，至今淨贏2席，從共和黨手中拿下佛羅里達州、弗吉尼亞州各1席。共和黨暫得70席。外界焦點在於民主黨今次可否拿下眾議院。眾議院435席會在中期選舉全部改選，過半數門檻為218席。"},{"pid":"5a3102496758a928471d804d0ef5f0c6dc319fe2","tid":892492,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T02:39:12.000Z","msg":"10：35 美匯指數由跌轉升，漲0.1%，報96.428。道指期貨漲超過130點。"},{"pid":"09f3fb6aa7a2929d006db38a26e7451f707a1897","tid":892492,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T02:41:15.000Z","msg":"１０：４０<br />\n<br />\n目前共和黨在參議院取得45席次，距離取得多數必須攻下的51席還差6席；民主黨目前則拿下34席。"},{"pid":"4372a9d06dfc04ed3afb2e8731f6bfb08ac87c45","tid":892492,"uid":69213,"like":3,"dislike":19,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T02:42:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bf103804e39a9921ec473cfd34fd1c70f26f5983","tid":892492,"uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T02:45:32.000Z","msg":"10：40 參議院搖擺州印第安納，共和黨候選人布勞恩（Mike Braun）預料獲勝，民主黨唐納利（Joe Donnelly）或連任失敗。<br />\n<br />\n10：42 參議院選戰，共和黨暫時淨贏1席，從民主黨手上奪得印第安納州席位，累計有46席，距51席多數還差5席。民主黨至今有34席。"},{"pid":"e5958095a27375c9318c6a5e1f0361affddef46b","tid":892492,"uid":134367,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T02:47:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/07/104717_a0546abf3bf40e7a93e6dd5b07a6eb4c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F07%2F104717_a0546abf3bf40e7a93e6dd5b07a6eb4c.jpg&h=41818cf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n要睇緊係睇外國網站"},{"pid":"43ad793df5f95c07bbcdc5f2a4fd72233ba8133c","tid":892492,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T03:11:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q4sCR9t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ4sCR9t.png&h=5ef082e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bba1ea739f3cef705298f21226fed810c72f15c0","tid":892492,"uid":18